Create an interview plan as a JSON object.
Rules: output JSON only.

Role: {{ role }}
Difficulty: {{ difficulty }}
Focus areas (raw text): {{ focus_areas }}
Prompt strategy name: {{ strategy_name }}
Interviewer persona: {{ persona }}

JSON schema (keys and expectations):
{
  "role": string,
  "difficulty": "Easy" | "Medium" | "Hard",
  "focus_areas": [string, ...],
  "total_questions": integer,
  "strategy": string,
  "persona": string,
  "rubric_criteria": [string, ...],
  "tips": [string, ...]
}

Constraints:
- focus_areas must be a clean list derived from the raw text.
- rubric_criteria must be practical for Software & AI Engineering interviews.
- tips must be actionable.
- total_questions MUST be exactly 5.